                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Conger</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-02-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 19, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay states that Mr. Conger’s action in regard to Waldersee’s order is
                    approved by the President, and his telegram of the 18th instant has been
                    communicated to the ambassadors of the United States at foreign courts.)</p>
            </div>
